overview:
Karthik Sethuraman is a communication designer working freelance to unleash his creative side.

Karthik Sethuraman provides solution to business owners and marketing professionals to spread out their business presence online, with top web design solutions, social media marketing and best seo services. Karthik Sethuraman have trained many web designers & top seo experts.

With striking SEO outcome and continuous analysis on search engine ranking metrics, Karthik Sethuraman had the opportunity to educate beginners and professionals in the field of search engine optimization. Always updated with the changes in search engine algorithms and modern advancements in web technology, he continues his knowledge sharing through his blog.

Yes, Karthik Sethuraman tweets, has friends and look after his official network. You know how to find him.
